Q: Yesterday was April 30, 2021. What is the date tomorrow in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
 If yesterday was April 30, 2021, then today is 04/30/2021. Tomorrow is 1 day in the future of today, which is 05/01/2021. So the answer is 05/01/2021.

