Q: Jane was born on the last day of Feburary in 2001. Today is her 16-year-old birthday. What is the date one week from today in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
 If Jane was born on the last day of February in 2001, then her birthday is 02/29/2001. Today is her 16-year-old birthday, which is 02/29/2017. One week from today is 7 days in the future of today, which is the 7th day of March 2017, or 03/07/2017. So the answer is 03/07/2017.

